It can also be used to massage the Achilles tendon and calf muscles. Primarily designed for targeting trigger points and addressing lower back discomfort. While it can be applied on either side of the spine, avoid direct contact with bones.

Primarily suited for larger muscle groups such as the glutes, hamstrings, and quadriceps. For stress relief and addressing pressure points, consider using it on the soles of your feet and around the upper back and neck area.
Crafted for gliding across broad muscle surfaces, this attachment is optimal for targeting dense muscle groups like the pectorals, glutes, and quadriceps.

Perfect for pinpointing localized muscle knots and tackling tension at its source. Ideal for precise muscle treatment and smaller muscle groups such as the soles of the feet, neck, and calves. Excellent for trigger point therapy but avoid prolonged use on any muscle area exceeding 15 seconds.

settings.text: Through continuous innovation and listening to our customers, we've transformed our tech into the pinnacle of reliability and convenience for your daily needs.

settings.accordion_question: How durable is the Titan Smart Cable?
settings.accordion_answer: Our cable is engineered with durability as a top priority. Constructed with triple nylon braiding and reinforced metal connector tips, it withstands up to 1,500 lbs of force, ensuring longevity that outlasts your device. Say goodbye to frayed or worn-out cables with Titan Power.

We have so much confidence in our cables durability that we offer a lifetime warranty and 60-day warranty on all other products. This means that if anything happens, we'll send you a brand new charger, free of charge! The warranty covers any defects in material or workmanship. Furthermore, if any unexpected or unreasonable damage occurs this will be covered. Any intentional damage or damage caused by unconventional use will not be covered. Please note that any cable sent out to you as a replacement will not be covered by this warranty.

settings.accordion_question: What devices are compatible with the Titan Smart Cables in the Nomad Bundle?
settings.accordion_answer: The Titan Smart Cables included in the Nomad Bundle are compatible with a wide range of devices, including smartphones, tablets, laptops, and more. They support both Android and iOS systems, making them versatile for all your charging needs.

settings.accordion_question: Is the 45W PD Plug suitable for international travel?
settings.accordion_answer: Yes, the 45W PD Plug included in the Nomad Bundle comes with attachments for US, EU, and UK sockets, making it perfect for international travel. You can charge your devices worldwide without worrying about compatibility issues.

settings.accordion_question: How portable is the Titan Travel Kit included in the Nomad Bundle?
settings.accordion_answer: The Titan Travel Kit is designed to be compact and lightweight, making it highly portable for travel. It fits easily into your bag or luggage, ensuring that you always have your charging accessories on hand wherever you go.

settings.accordion_question: What are the benefits of using the Titan Massage Gun while traveling?
settings.accordion_answer: The Titan Massage Gun provides effective relief from muscle soreness, stiffness, and tension, making it ideal for travelers. It helps alleviate discomfort after long flights or extended periods of sitting, allowing you to stay refreshed and rejuvenated during your journeys.

settings.accordion_question: Is The Massage Gun Easy To Use For Someone With No Experience?
settings.accordion_answer: Absolutely, our Titan Power Massage Gun is designed with simplicity in mind, suitable for both beginners and professionals.
